Package: AHD
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Hellinger Distance for Testing Independence
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jiujing", "Wu", email = "jiujingwu@foxmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")), 
    person("Wenwen", "Guo", email = "guowenwen114@163.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: Implements the Adaptive Hellinger Distance (AHD) index and perform a permutation test for testing independence between two random vectors. 
          It includes functions for computing the AHD statistic, conducting permutation test, and combining p-values. 
